{"tid":1443060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀被捕少女懷疑被胸襲 - GIF圖逐格分析","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:13:38.000Z","uid":293282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a746ebedbd628d5c6612f3e63e31d29f0e0210d","tid":1443060,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"呢篇野本來來自我係另一個post (  <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441331</a>  )既回覆，但寫得幾長，所以開新post另外討論。<br />\n-----------------------------------<br />\n我做了一些分析，我先將最關鍵的影片斬為671幅圖，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我係逐格睇既</span></span>。<br />\n關鍵在於呢幾幅:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/914qbhQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F914qbhQ.png&h=74eab779&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖383 (警察右手手掌在少女右胸前方)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YYeanpG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYYeanpG.png&h=121fdb80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖386(警察右手手掌伸至少女左胸前方，並比之前靠近。有所動作。)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aq4d4Dg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faq4d4Dg.png&h=91f946b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖387(手掌向前向下繼續邁進。)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OcEBhYv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcEBhYv.png&h=dc2d0221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖388（另一警察大開手臂阻擋鏡頭）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw77pDE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw77pDE.png&h=bd059789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖389<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxyqVLx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxyqVLx.png&h=d031e2c4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖390<br />\n若果製作成gif，將會如下:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFsvnqY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFsvnqY.gif&h=3b0069c0&s={S